      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and benefits from a recently overhauled Double VANOS system. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the factory M-Variable differential. The chassis remains rigid with documented subframe reinforcement, and the suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for neutral handling characteristics. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-driven enthusiast vehicle, the drivetrain is dialed in for peak performance.",
